text: Choristella ponderi is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Choristellidae. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off New South Wales, Australia. ==References== ==External links== * McLean J.H. (1992). Systematic review of the family Choristellidae (Archeogastropoda: Lepetellacea) with descriptions of new species. The Veliger 35(4): 273-294 Category:Choristellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1992
title: Choristella ponderi
